Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:24.34,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}任何人都在迷茫中寻觅答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:44.47,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}曾以为二人同心　时间也可支配
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:52.46,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}当岁月流逝　天空不再湛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:57.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心与心渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:05.35,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}周而复始　季节循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:11.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}愿时光　永远停留在那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:18.11,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}二人仍迷茫着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:27.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}在天边寻找各自真爱的岁月…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)\an3}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)\an3}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哲学家的话说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事物没有偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部由必然构成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们截获的这条情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是必然的造物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「战争必须获胜才有意义」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这虽是帕特里克·萨拉的口头禅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这么想的人恐怕不只他一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也不是 在为失败而战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方皆有正义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且无法调和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上战场的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各个为自己的正义杀敌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争的最大导火索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血色情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为报复核打击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特四处布设中子干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗称N干扰的作用下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方均无法使用核武
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当核引擎、核武器退出战场舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取而代之的战争之王变成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扎夫特开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为机动战士的特种机动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只拥有旧式战斗机的泛生机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动堡垒的地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为开发机动战士不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦情有可原
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 封印核武不意味着战争结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如和平的象征 白鸽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其不拥有一击必杀的尖喙利爪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦开战 其景象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往往更加漫长而凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们与它 何其相似
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异类 神秘的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差异招来不安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终化作仇恨互相敌视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切始于那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治·格兰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁获得MIT博士学位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥林匹克银牌获得者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美式橄榄球明星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空军王牌驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在航空宇宙工程学领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也荣获诸多殊荣的这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为全世界人瞩目的焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们期待着他下一个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是 木星探测任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他驾驶自己设计的宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始踏上单程7年的星空之旅时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从轨道上发来这样一段话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 现在公开我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非 人类自然孕育
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生在这世界上的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在受精卵阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受过人工基因改造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就将其详细技术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全世界网络公开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如他所说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拥有比自然出生之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更强健的身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和更聪明的头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他的创造者曾经对他说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类 还有无尽的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能将它最大限度发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的前途不可限量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这片宇宙空间俯瞰地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次让我想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是连接这颗母亲般的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和未知宇宙之间的桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在人类现在与未来之间的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整者 Coordinator
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正应该如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我后继有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他留下这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾着飞船消失在星海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而将技术与混乱 留给了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14年后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他再次为我们带来另一个「震惊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为调查这块来自宇宙的馈赠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将离开地面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们的研究卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终将把资源、技术等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种宇宙的恩泽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赠还于地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扩大战火有何益处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以更无法饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是国家、语言、价值观、身世、信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个千差万别的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又带来了怎样的差别呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当亲身体会到 也为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蓝色纯净的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要和你握手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人少来厚颜无耻地套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人之根源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使尽在掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍改变不了人的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美者不知缺陷者之苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺陷者嫉恨完美者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:20.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an2\pos(640,620)\fs60}中子干扰器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是谁践踏了这份向往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是谁 为了一己私欲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们调整人实施压迫和榨取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异类 与自己不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又可爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是基拉 基拉是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎奈枪膛中放出的炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不会传达那份温情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国防委员会 萨拉议长来电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是必须与之战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因此才有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,0)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}各自的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满身是汗 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧还是不退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生到底去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉 基拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯加在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们现在在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是挑了个好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特势力圈的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能置强袭于不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算那样降落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰与强袭 突入角有差异
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这样下去会大幅偏离降落地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不来吗 快回船上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能了 凭强袭自己的推进力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船靠上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号的喷射器还可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这样船的降落点也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去强袭没有意义 快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 本舰的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及目的地不变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大副呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰如果葬身此处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八舰队的牺牲将全部白费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看那孩子 然后上床睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也早点歇了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长这么精疲力尽的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是感染引起的高烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内脏也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有让他多摄取水分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能给身体降温
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也是第一次给调整人看病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能百分百打包票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们跟我们比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体机能好的不是一点半点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看上去相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的性能完全是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远比我们强壮的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和远比我们聪明的头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不会患上绝症
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗力也高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 不是刀枪不入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但风险比我们低多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他驾驶舱里的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高升到过多少度 听说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换成我们的话 早翘辫子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以发个烧算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是弗拉戈 进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 有什么情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟他们解释
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性能完全不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:13:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克他们听说安全着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才接到联络
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过归期还未定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时滞留直布罗陀基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克的伤怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多操心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时那么激烈的战斗都挺过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我担心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到头来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既未能摧毁也未能捕获强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那艘新船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以队长又被召回了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽队长也未能击落的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委员会看在眼里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长这次回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也是因为有其他作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看下迅雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 还不能坐起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上的医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉回船的时候已经失去意识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球 沙漠里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上降落的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体有点意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还能装强袭装备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我当快递员？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 上尉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 少校的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天涯海角也能送到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是哈尔巴顿提督一番好意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状况下升迁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涨得工资 什么时候能用？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小孩算火线任命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼是少尉来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 其他也全是二等兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙学得很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那孩子的烧退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说早上刚退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知该说强袭厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是他身体厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 基拉为什么有时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那东西叫作高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 启动画面上有写
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,General
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unilateral
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neuro-link什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头文字连在一起的读音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队里简称「G」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说没事了 已经回房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭菜芙蕾端去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换班？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真的已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭也吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我们都在瞎操心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船医让他今天继续躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不同啊 身体的素质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好吗 没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚一直陪着基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭已经和基拉一起吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不像大家 有船上的勤务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得让基拉早点好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有点担心他 我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 先别走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛 和你的事是爸爸决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸现在也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是刚提起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们周围的情况也变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想没必要再被那件事束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说驾驶神盾的是你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 我赢了那场赌局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉必须战斗战斗 战斗到死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则决不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这可真是不速之客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽放跑了的飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来暂时不会无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达克斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维修人员让我把这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭驾驶室里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是基拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大哥哥保护我们
